- cs.IT (Information Theory) is relevant as the paper considers packet latency and injection rates. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possibility as the paper deals with controlling the behavior of an adversary. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses the properties of different algorithms.
